{"tid":829880,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[116巴士]一時衝動 將失物執咗返屋企，而家點算好，點揾返物主","createTime":"2018-09-20T19:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T17:14:46.000Z","uid":39971,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"718c7a24521086b656f428220b3023229589f631","tid":829880,"uid":39971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:24:20.000Z","msg":"今日大概19:00係116巴士上層執到 <br />\n一個現代教育嘅繩索袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/021448_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F021448_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ce7b5177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入面有:<br />\n1.一件金文泰中學嘅運動服上衣<br />\n2.一包virjoy紙巾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/021750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F021750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8b0e5298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係就快落車之際，經過一番激烈嘅思想鬥爭，一時衝動之下，決定親手還比物主，於是我將個袋攞埋落車。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我帶住個袋，去咗我本來專登搭116嚟嘅目的地 慈雲山食車仔麵，飲埋芒椰仙草<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/023343_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F023343_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5a10ccbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完嘢 搭緊車返觀塘嘅時候<br />\n我發現。。。我成身都係車仔麵味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最重要嘅係 嗰位現代中學狗個袋成浸餸味。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都唔想㗎嘛 於是我無再怪自己<br />\n<br />\n咁食到飽晒<br />\n當然就到去埋ff跑步<br />\n做完運動 我發現啲俾我香汗淋漓過嘅衫無位放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁啱我瞄到中學雞個袋有大量位<br />\n於是我就放咗落。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是我繼續行返屋企<br />\n竟然發現協和街個坐係街邊賣水果嘅阿婆<br />\n今日竟然有百香果賣 我係觀塘街市摷咗幾次都無 今日仲要$10有6/7隻!<br />\n唔係講笑 百香果整特飲真係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我即係入手兩草<br />\n好順手咁放埋入現代狗袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/030623_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F030623_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=77a491e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/031246_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F031246_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=146ebc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企 我為咗表示歉意<br />\n我啱啱手洗咗佢啲校服同繩索袋<br />\n仲加咗幾滴柑橘味熊寶貝 洗完好撚香<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但而家問題係我點還返個袋失物比佢<br />\n定就咁攞番落巴士總站比站長<br />\n暫時線索<br />\n1.讀金文泰中學<br />\n2.有補過現代教育<br />\n3.搭116返屋企"},{"pid":"6eb6dc93b6859219c8674bf798cab9dc3e6ed2b4","tid":829880,"uid":49055,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪鍾意將事情複雜化？"},{"pid":"c5d54acfca0d54875aef015d8d6253389a820f52","tid":829880,"uid":39971,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6eb6dc93b6859219c8674bf798cab9dc3e6ed2b4","tid":829880,"uid":49055,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪鍾意將事情複雜化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:39:22.000Z","msg":"ching,我，執，到，袋。"},{"pid":"dfd0e39ec336fcea2263e0afdc82027d90006842","tid":829880,"uid":87043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:54:01.000Z","msg":"幾好笑..."},{"pid":"ef17ab137759f21822c5421600b5ff63dc76e821","tid":829880,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:58:42.000Z","msg":"好想打飛機"},{"pid":"b5642b29a89dae938a4098bc4c50bced8d20129f","tid":829880,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T20:01:49.000Z","msg":"拎左件衫打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4872317e162dd9744c296dcb1e4d621300f29c","tid":829880,"uid":40550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T20:11:14.000Z","msg":"你拎去金文泰同校務講低邊到幾時執到<br />\n佢地開咪一搵就搵到啦<br />\n<br />\n不過就無得FF撞到靚女"},{"pid":"71d0e672939597afa79a7c6e35d76d0416039f49","tid":829880,"uid":101253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T20:38:28.000Z","msg":"仲有無第二集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b863b1a2cedf324a24eb168f5750b99666fe1efe","t